[
    {
        "id": "Minecraft Java Edition 安装教程",
        "title": "Minecraft Java Edition 安装教程",
        "author": "Oringes",
        "date": "2025-06-28",
        "version": "所有版本",
        "thumbnail": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/MC-OV-logo_300x300.png",
        "shortDescription": "《我的世界》（Minecraft）是一款沙盒类电子游戏。",
        "tags": ["沙盒游戏", "客户端", "服务端", "单人", "多人", "Mods"],
        "content": [
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/简介.png"

            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "简介",
                "level": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Minecraft Java Edition是一款由 Mojang Studios 开发的沙盒游戏，于2009年11月18日发布。"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "准备工作",
                "level": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "list",
                "items":[
                    "一台可以上网的电脑",
                    "支付宝并且里面还有 ¥89",
                    "一个可以使用并可以接收到消息的邮箱账号",
                    "准备一个密码"
                ]
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "第一部分：注册&登录你的微软账号",
                "level": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "打开你的微软商店（Microsoft Store），点击右上角登录"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/1.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/2.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Microsoft Store 会自动关联已经登录 Windows 设备的微软账户，如果你已经拥有此账户，则直接点击登录即可，若不想使用该账户登录，则点击下面的“使用其他账户”选项。"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/3.png"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "选择后，点击下方的继续按钮，等待跳转。"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/4.png"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "下面也不再过多的赘述，请自行查看<a href='https://support.microsoft.com/zh-cn/account-billing/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E6%96%B0%E7%9A%84-microsoft-%E5%B8%90%E6%88%B7-a84675c3-3e9e-17cf-2911-3d56b15c0aaf'>官方文档</a>。"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "第二部分：在 Microsoft Store 中搜索 Minecraft",
                "level": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "blockquote",
                "text": ">>> 请注意，以下步骤均需要在已经登录 Microsoft 账号后进行 <<<"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "1. 打开的 Microsoft Store",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "2. 搜索栏输入“Minecraft”，回车搜索（或者鼠标点击“放大镜”小箭头）",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/5.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "3. 点击“Minecraft：Java & Minecraft Bedrock Edition for PC”。",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/6.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "4. 点击购买（售价 ¥89）。",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/7.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "第三部分：购买",
                "level": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "1. 在付款方式中选择 支付宝，然后点击购买",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/8.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/9.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "2. 添加您的支付宝，下一页",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/10.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "3. 如果是第一次在 Microsoft Store 购买物品，则会弹出下面的窗口，此时打开你的支付宝，扫码绑定，成功后点击下方“继续”按钮",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "blockquote",
                "text": ">>> 如果你已经在 Microsoft Store 上购买过物品，则可能不会出现下面的弹窗，请直接跳转步骤 4 <<<"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/11.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "4. 在支付宝界面你会签约微软免密支付，点击“同意协议并开通免密支付”",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/12.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "5. 开通后在 Microsoft Store 里点击继续，填写你的收货地址，填写完以后点击保存",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "blockquote",
                "text": ">>> 不需要填写很详细，随便填写就好，地址不会对购买有任何影响。 <<<"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/13.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "6. 点击“购买”按钮，随后就会进行静默扣款，你可以在支付宝中看到交易记录",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/14.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/15.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "恭喜你拥有了Minecraft Java正版帐号了！"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "第四部分：下载官方启动器 Minecraft Launcher 安装包",
                "level": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "1. 回到微软商店，点击安装，下载，安装",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/16.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/17.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/18.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "2. 耐心等待安装完成",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/19.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "3. 在开始菜单中找到刚刚安装好的Minecraft，点击Minecraft Launcher",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/20.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "4. 点击下方“SGIN IN WITH MINECRAFT”进行登录，请注意，您登录的微软账号需要是购买时的账号。",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/21.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "5. 若为首次登录，则会弹出如下窗口，请输入你的 Xbox 昵称（注意！一旦设置无法修改！），设置好后点击“下一步”。",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "blockquote",
                "text": ">>> 请注意，若之前已经拥有XBOX账户，则该弹窗不会出现。 <<<"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/22.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "6. 你可以选择是否发送可选数据，设置好后点击“现在就开始吧”—“下一步”",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/23.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/24.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "7. 欢迎进入Minecraft的奇妙世界！",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/25.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "第五部分：设置你的 Minecraft ID",
                "level": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "<a href='https://www.minecraft.net/zh-hans'>Minecraft 官网</a>"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "1. 打开 Minecraft 官网，点击“继续浏览该网站”（智障冈易）",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "blockquote",
                "text": ">>> 请注意，若再次出现此类提示，继续点击“继续浏览该网站”！！！ <<<"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/26.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "2. 右上角“账户”—“登录”，登录你刚刚购买的账号",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/27.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/28.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "之后就按照引导进行登录即可。"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "3. 在下面找到点击“档案名称”，自己设置就好",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/29.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/30.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "设置完成后，你还可以自行在此页面进行皮肤的更换和披风的开启！"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "第六部分：安装第三方启动器",
                "level": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "blockquote",
                "text": ">>> 官方启动器无法加载Fabric、Forge和Mod扩展，此时第三方启动器可以很好的解决这个问题。<<<"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": " "
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "什么是Fabric和Forge？"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "Forge 和 Fabric 是 Minecraft 中两种主要的 Mod 加载器，它们各自有不同的特点和适用场景。Forge 是一种老牌的 Mod 加载器，适用于 Minecraft 的多个版本。它的主要特点是大型和封闭。Fabric 是一种较新的 mod 加载器，适用于 Minecraft 的较新版本。它的主要特点是模块化和开放。"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "1. 下载HMCL (Hello Minecraft Launcher)启动器",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "<a href='https://hmcl.huangyuhui.net/download/'>HMCL官网下载链接</a>"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "记住访问密码为“5267”。"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/31.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "2. 输入访问密码后，点击“HMCL-X.X.XX.zip”的标签，并且用普通下载方式下载",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/32.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/33.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "3. 下载完成后，在“C:/Users/[你的用户名]/Downloads/”下，找到下载的压缩包文件，解压",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/34.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "先在“C:/”下创建一个名为“Minecraft”的文件夹，然后在回到刚刚解压的文件夹目录下，将“HMCL-X.X.XX.exe”文件复制到“C:/Minecraft”文件夹下。"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/35.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/36.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "在打开“C:/Minecraft”文件夹后，点击运行“HMCL-X.X.XX.exe”文件。"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "4. 运行HMCL启动器，并且登录刚刚购买了Minecraft正版的账号",
                "level": 3
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/37.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/38.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/39.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "记住这里的验证代码如“BHCQSSGF”，待自动跳转到浏览器中进行验证的时候，按照提示输入验证代码。"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/40.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/41.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "text": "然后点击下方的“允许访问”按钮，之后进行身份验证即可。"
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/42.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "heading",
                "text": "恭喜！在完成验证后，现在你可以开始你的完整版Minecraft之旅 和 无数Mod的扩展内容了！",
                "level": 2
            },
            {
                "type": "image",
                "src": "./images/Minecraft-Java-Edition-安装教程/43.webp"
            },
            {
                "type": "blockquote",
                "text": ">>> 在接下来的Minecraft之旅中你将学习到如何设置启动器，如何安装Mod加载器，如何管理你的mod文件，等等的技能。这是一个漫长的旅行，你会一次次的碰到代码启动失败，并一次次通过浏览器访问，来搜索解决方案；你会一次次的碰到客户端与服务端链接同步的问题，并一次次尝试增删文件来解决问题；无论什么，最终的你都将得到Minecraft所带来的一切！一切问题都可以被解决的。 <<<"
            }

        ]
    },
